                "title": "Spiritfox Sin-Eater"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Summons 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Sesshou Sakura</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/d61b58a8c379e509cbdf1570518cc5e7_8627162816509965612.png",
                "id": "talent91693",
                "key": "Yakan Evocation: Sesshou Sakura",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Yakan Evocation: Sesshou Sakura"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>. If your side of the field has any <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Sesshou Sakura</span>, destroy them and create <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tenko Thunderbolts</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Tenko Thunderbolts</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Combat Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Before you choose your action</span>: Deal 3 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/a7087fbd0fdda01da0e66ebec47d5b17_2110638969769360149.png",
                "id": "talent12400",
                "key": "Great Secret Art: Tenko Kenshin ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Great Secret Art: Tenko Kenshin "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">End Phase</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 3</span> (Can stack, max 6 stacks)</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">When you declare the end of your Round</span>: If this summon has at least 4 Usage(s) remaining, deal 1 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>. (Consumes Usage(s))</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3948777244555788393.png",
                "id": "talent67558",
                "key": "Sesshou Sakura",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/35428890/9935fc2ef27a255d96756090578adee7_2392656634270445399.png",
                "title": "Sesshou Sakura"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Electro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_4934142757994381349.png",
                "id": "talent71292",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/20/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_4685283001004704078.png",
